<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="zh" munual-autotracker-init="" qct-uid="" qct-pv-id="nj-talzZaSYi4QiAqXCxu" qct-ip="2a02:c207:3019:5236::1" style="background:#ffffff;overscroll-behavior:auto;height:100%"><head><meta charSet="UTF-8"/><meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/><meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no"/><title>ISSCC 2026：Nvidia展示7nm EIC＋65nm PIC混合键合的256Gb/s DWDM 3D堆叠CPO光互连芯片-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云</title><meta name="subject" content="其他-空类-设计,其他-空类-数据,其他-空类-芯片,其他-空类-nvidia,其他-空类-pic"/><meta name="subjectTime" content="2026-03-02 21:54:41"/><meta name="articleSource" content="W"/><meta name="magicSource" content="N"/><meta name="authorType" content="Z"/><meta name="productSlug" content="none"/><meta name="authorUID" content="11573193"/><meta name="keywords" content="DWDM光链路,时钟转发,3D堆叠工艺,共封装光学"/><meta name="description" content="NVIDIA团队创新推出半速率带通滤波时钟转发DWDM光链路，采用3D堆叠工艺实现256Gb/s单光纤吞吐量。该设计融合转发时钟与嵌入式时钟优势，通过带通滤波技术有效抑制抖动，实现2.78pJ/b全系统能效和1.33Tbps/mm²高集成密度，满足AI数据中心对高速、低功耗光互连的迫切需求。"/><meta property="og:title" content="ISSCC 2026：Nvidia展示7nm EIC＋65nm PIC混合键合的256Gb/s DWDM 3D堆叠CPO光互连芯片-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云"/><meta property="og:description" content="NVIDIA团队创新推出半速率带通滤波时钟转发DWDM光链路，采用3D堆叠工艺实现256Gb/s单光纤吞吐量。该设计融合转发时钟与嵌入式时钟优势，通过带通滤波技术有效抑制抖动，实现2.78pJ/b全系统能效和1.33Tbps/mm²高集成密度，满足AI数据中心对高速、低功耗光互连的迫切需求。"/><meta property="og:image" content="https://cloudcache.tencent-cloud.com/open_proj/proj_qcloud_v2/gateway/shareicons/cloud.png"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1, viewport-fit=cover"/><meta name="referrer" content="unsafe-url"/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//qccommunity.qcloudimg.com"/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//ask.qcloudimg.com"/><link rel="dns-prefetch" href="//cloudcache.tencent-cloud.com"/><link rel="canonical" href="https://cloud.tencent.cn/developer/article/2633146"/><meta name="next-head-count" content="22"/><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://imgcache.qq.com/open_proj/proj_qcloud_v2/gateway/portal/css/base.cs